"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/the-tao-of-the-backup-catcher-review-roughing-it-on-the-diamond-3f9dfd1e?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">替补捕手之道：为热爱棒球而打球</a></h3><div class="media-object scope-
